<view class="page route-form-page"><view class="form-header"><view class="form-header-title">{{a}}</view><view class="form-header-desc">请准确填写线路的起止省市、报价及时效信息。</view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">托运路线</view><view class="field"><text class="label">线路类型</text><view class="input" style="line-height:88rpx;background-color:#e2e8f0;color:#475569">{{b}}</view></view><view class="field"><text class="label">出发城市 <text class="required">*</text></text><view class="picker-display" bindtap="{{f}}"><text wx:if="{{c}}">{{d}} · {{e}}</text><text wx:else style="color:#9ca3af">选择出发省份与城市</text></view></view><view class="field"><text class="label">目的城市 <text class="required">*</text></text><view class="picker-display" bindtap="{{j}}"><text wx:if="{{g}}">{{h}} · {{i}}</text><text wx:else style="color:#9ca3af">选择目的省份与城市</text></view></view><view class="field"><text class="label">预计运输时效 <text class="required">*</text></text><input class="input" placeholder="例如: 2-3天 / 当天送达" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{k}}" bindinput="{{l}}"/></view><view wx:if="{{m}}" class="field"><text class="label">展示状态 <text class="required">*</text></text><view class="grid-two"><view class="{{['check-row', o && 'checked']}}" bindtap="{{p}}"><text class="radio-icon-box">{{n}}</text><text>开启展示中</text></view><view class="{{['check-row', r && 'checked']}}" bindtap="{{s}}"><text class="radio-icon-box">{{q}}</text><text>暂时关闭</text></view></view></view></view><view wx:if="{{t}}" class="section"><view class="section-title">大板报价配置</view><view class="field"><text class="label">固定参考报价 (元) (选填，空表示电话沟通)</text><input class="input" type="digit" placeholder="请输入该线路每台车固定参考运费" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{v}}" bindinput="{{w}}"/></view></view><view wx:if="{{x}}" class="section"><view class="section-title">小板起步及公里阶梯报价</view><view class="field"><text class="label">起步参考价 (元) (选填，空表示电话沟通)</text><input class="input" type="digit" placeholder="例如: 350" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{y}}" bindinput="{{z}}"/></view><view class="field"><text class="label">起步包含公里数 (公里) (选填)</text><input class="input" type="number" placeholder="例如: 10" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{A}}" bindinput="{{B}}"/></view><view class="field"><text class="label">超出起步后的公里阶梯价模板</text><picker mode="selector" range="{{D}}" range-key="templateName" bindchange="{{E}}"><view class="picker-display"><text>{{C}}</text></view></picker><view class="subtle" style="margin-top:16rpx;color:#1677ff" bindtap="{{F}}"> 🏷️ 管理我的阶梯价模板 ❯ </view></view></view><region-picker wx:if="{{I}}" class="r" u-r="regionPicker" bindselect="{{H}}" u-i="3f7861a2-0" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{I}}"/><view class="fixed-footer"><button class="primary-btn animate-btn" loading="{{J}}" bindtap="{{K}}"> 保存线路配置 </button></view></view>